<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>رادار الكوموندو - الإصدار الاحترافي</title>
    <style>
        :root { --neon-green: #39ff14; --dark-bg: #0a0a0a; }
        body { background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: var(--neon-green); font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; overflow: hidden; }
        
        header { 
            background: #000; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--neon-green);
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        .status-dot { height: 10px; width: 10px; background-color: red; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; animation: blink 1s infinite; }
        @keyframes blink { 0% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.3; } 100% { opacity: 1; } }

        .tabs-bar { display: flex; background: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; }
        .tab-btn { 
            flex: 1; padding: 15px; border: none; background: none; color: #888; 
            cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.3s; font-size: 14px;
        }
        .tab-btn.active { color: var(--neon-green); background: #222; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--neon-green); }

        .content { height: calc(100vh - 120px); width: 100%; }
        .radar-frame { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; display: none; }
        .radar-frame.active { display: block; }

        footer { position: fixed; bottom: 0; width: 100%; background: #000; font-size: 10px; padding: 5px; color: #555; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div>🛰️ نظام رادار الكوموندو</div>
    <div><span class="status-dot"></span> LIVE DATA</div>
</header>

<div class="tabs-bar">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="changeRadar(event, 'nasa')">صور الأقمار (NASA)</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="changeRadar(event, 'rain')">الأمطار والبرق</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="changeRadar(event, 'wind')">حركة الرياح (Windy)</button>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <iframe id="nasa" class="radar-frame active" src="https://worldview.earthdata.nasa.gov/?v=-24.4,24.5,23.3,47.8&l=Reference_Labels_15m,Coastlines_15m,VIIRS_SNPP_CorrectedReflectance_TrueColor&t=2026-03-22"></iframe>
    
    <iframe id="rain" class="radar-frame" src="https://www.rainviewer.com/map.html?loc=24.5,45,5&type=radar&o=1&c=7&g=1&s=1&p=1"></iframe>
    
    <iframe id="wind" class="radar-frame" src="https://www.windy.com/?24.447,46.706,5"></iframe>
</div>

<footer>إشارة مشفرة - تحديث تلقائي عبر الأقمار الصناعية</footer>

<script>
    function changeRadar(evt, radarId) {
        var frames = document.getElementsByClassName("radar-frame");
        for (var i = 0; i < frames.length; i++) { frames[i].classList.remove("active"); }
        
        var btns = document.getElementsByClassName("tab-btn");
        for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) { btns[i].classList.remove("active"); }
        
        document.getElementById(radarId).classList.add("active");
        evt.currentTarget.classList.add("active");
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
